# Tasks: gentle-ai-nixos-vanilla-integration

## Phase 1: Version Pinning (Foundation)

- [ ] 1.1 Pin `gentle-ai-src` URL in `flake.nix` to tag `v1.21.0`: `url = "github:Gentleman-Programming/gentle-ai/v1.21.0"`
- [ ] 1.2 Add comment in `flake.nix` documenting binary↔source version correspondence: `# Must match version in pkgs/gentle-ai/default.nix`
- [ ] 1.3 Run `nix flake lock --update-input gentle-ai-src` to regenerate `flake.lock`

## Phase 2: Vanilla Derivation (Core)

- [ ] 2.1 Create `pkgs/gentle-ai-assets/vanilla.nix` with signature `{ lib, stdenvNoCC, gentle-ai-src }:`
- [ ] 2.2 Implement `installPhase` using only `cp` operations to copy: `AGENTS.md`, `internal/assets/skills/*` (16 skills), `internal/assets/opencode/*` (commands, plugins, persona, opencode.json template), agent configs (`claude`, `cursor`, `windsurf`, `gemini`, `codex`, `kimi`, `qwen`, `kiro`), root `skills/*`
